              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Energy-spectrum of tritons at 0.Deg"
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".The peak at 10.3 MeV in the triton spectrum can be",
                " interpreted as the following reaction",
                " neutron +Li7 = triton + He5(ground)",
                "                         He5(ground) = He4 + neutron",
                ".The continuous part of the triton spectrum can not be",
                " explained only by the assumption of the reaction",
                " neutron +Li7 = neutron  + Li7(4.63MeV)",
                "                           Li7(4.63MeV) = alpha +triton",
                ".The contributions of the reactions",
                " neutron +Li7 = He4 + H4",
                "                      H4  = neutron + triton",
                " neutron +Li7 = triton + He5(2.6 Or 5.MeV)",
                "                         He5(2.6 Or 5.MeV)=He4 +neutron",
                " may also play some role.",
                ". The dip in the triton spectrum does not allow for",
                "  a three-body breakup without final state interaction",
                "  between them."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "HISTORY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
